                            <comment id="70879" author="adilger" created="Wed, 6 Nov 2013 17:39:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;In newer versions of Lustre there is the &quot;lctl replace_nids&quot; command that could change the NID.  In older versions of Lustre it is necessary to run --writeconf to rewrite the whole configuration.  Please see the manual for details.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
